As seguintes classes já concluíram a transferência de 1ª classe.
A classe Mística inclui todos os magos e curandeiros.

Classe Guerreiros
Warrior, Knight, Rogue, Gladiator, Paladin, Warlord, Dark Avenger, Treasure Hunter, Hawkeye, Elven Knight, Elven Scout, Temple Knight, Swordsinger, Plain Walker, Silver Ranger, Palus Knight, Assassin, Shilien Knight, Blade Dancer, Abyss Walker, Phantom Ranger, Orc Raider, Orc Monk, Destroyer, Tyrant, Scavenger, Artisan, Bounty Hunter, Warsmith, Trooper, Warder, Berserker, Soul Breaker e Arbalester.
Classe Mística
Wizard, Sorcerer, Necromancer, Warlock, Elven Wizard, Spellsinger, Elemental Summoner, Dark Wizard, Spellhowler e Phantom Summoner.
Classe Curandeiros
Cleric, Bishop, Prophet, Oracle, Elder, Shilien Oracle, Shilien Elder, Orc Shaman, Overlord, Warcryer e Inspector.
